# BT/P2P 客户端进程拦截规则
# 强制 BT 客户端所有流量走直连，避免经过代理服务器

# =====================
# qBittorrent
# =====================
PROCESS-NAME,qbittorrent.exe
PROCESS-NAME,qbittorrent
PROCESS-NAME,qbittorrent-nox
PROCESS-NAME,qbittorrent-nox.exe

